divs: sighting detailsi live on the space coast of fla, 'n i have seen a lot of strange objects in the sky, usually at night. one afternoon i was sitting in my back yard, taking pics of my tropical plants, when i heard a buzzing\humming sound to the north. the sky was overcast, i looked up in the direction and saw a kind of a barrel shape floating. i took some pics w' my digital cam but they didn't seem to register. i also had a 110mm cam which i also shot a pic to the north. i followed the sound toward the east 'n snapped a pic as it went behind some trees. it then was heading south 'n came out into the clearing 'n i snapped another pic. it then kinda leaned forward 'n took off really fast heading west. when i came into my house i tried to download my digital cam but it was blank except for the flower pics. my 110mm had a 24 film roll 'n at this time there were 10 snaps. i used the cam over 5 yrs 'n when the roll was used up, i had it developed. i had thought maybe the pics didn't come out like the digital. i was surprised when they looked so clear. as i was watching this thing, i suddenly knew how they move, how they beat gravity. the pics i enclosed were scaned, i have original films.
